pageProduct.name: OsteVit D & Calcium 1 A Day 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

OsteVit-D One-A-Day Vitamin D3 & Calcium chewable tablet in a pleasant tasting French Vanilla flavour.

OsteVit-D One-A-Day Vitamin D3 & Calcium supports bone desnisty & strength.

Size: 60 Chewable Tablets

KEY FEATURES

• • Vitamin D enhances calcium absorpbtion
• • Calcium supports bone density and strength
• • Aids muscle development and supports muscle function
• • Supports healthy immune system function
• • Suitable for vegetarians
• • Free From: Gluten, Lactose, Yeast, Gelatin Artificial colours

Warnings

Vitamins can only be of assistance if dietary vitamin intake is inadequate.
Contains Sugar

Ingredients

Acacia, dl-alpha-tocopherol , Flavour, glucose monohydrate, magnesium stearate, maize starch, maltodextrin, medium chain triglycerides, microcrystalline cellulose, silicon dioxide, sucrose

Active Ingredients: Each chewable tablet contains 1000 IU of Vitamin D3 (cholecalciferol 25 micrograms) and 600 mg of elemental calcium (calcium carbonate 1.5g)

Directions

For adults and children over 12 years of age: Chew 1 tablet daily or as directed by your healthcare professional.

Children under 12 years of age: As directed by your healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C
